            <div class="panel panel-default">
                <div class="panel-heading">
                    <h4 class="panel-title">
                        <a data-toggle="collapse" data-parent="#accordion" href="#collapse3">
                            What is originstamp.org?</a>
                    </h4>
                </div>
                <div id="collapse3" class="panel-collapse collapse">
                    <div class="panel-body">
                        Originstamp is a decentralized trusted timestamping service, which makes use of the Bitcoin blockchain.
                        A trusted timestamp verfies that a files content existed at a certain time. Thus its important to
                        keep the timestamped file unmodified. The content addressed files in IPFS supports them, since they are not alterable.
                        Decentralized trusted timestamping uses a unique fingerprint of the data (hash) and submits that to the blockchain. Once the fingerprint
                        is in the blockchain, it can't be manipulated and is tamperproof.

                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

